The album, in AngieGurumi's Gallery,  
called Amigurumi Knitted Collection contains, 43 scanned images of the  
first page of Alan Dart's copyrighted knitting patterns. Her email is  
mentioned, together with a note not to leave messages on the page. This
use  
of the images infringes Alan's copyright, is illegal and adversely affects
 
his livelihood.. Below is the url of the album.
